OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FPolitical Correspondant Lise McNally
OL,7,Fhas been speaking to a North West
OL,8,Ffamily about what changes they want to
OL,9,Fsee to paternity leave
OL,11,FFathers are urging the Government to
OL,12,Fprovide better paternity leave - amid
OL,13,Fwarnings that current offer is one of
OL,14,Fthe worst in Europe.
OL,16,FScott Ramage from Walkden is one of
OL,17,Fhundreds who have backed The Dad
OL,18,FShift's campaign. His baby son had
OL,19,Fonly just left intensive care when he
OL,20,Fwas forced to go back to work - a
OL,21,Fsystem he says is broken and brutal.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/14
