OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FScott's son Tyler was born two weeks
OL,7,Fearly by emergency c-section, he ended
OL,8,Fup with a condition called neutropenic
OL,9,Fsepsis and had to stay in intensive
OL,10,Fcare for the first ten days of his
OL,11,Flife. Scott's wife Louise was also
OL,12,Fbeing treated for sepsis, and trying
OL,13,Fto recover from a traumatic labour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/14
