OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FScott says "My paternity leave was
OL,7,Fspent with us stuck at the Royal
OL,8,FBolton Hospital, trying to split
OL,9,Fmyself between being with Tyler on the
OL,10,Fneonatal unit and trying to support
OL,11,FLouise as much as a I could do -
OL,12,Fbecause she was on the ward upstairs
OL,13,Frecovering from a c-section after
OL,14,Fbeing in labour for 69 hours. It was
OL,15,Fquite a traumatic time really - it was
OL,16,Freally difficult. You don't get much
OL,17,Ftime to adjust as a family."
OL,19,FWhat is the statuatory paternity leave?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/14
