OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FEligible mothers on maternity leave
OL,7,Freceive 90% of their average weekly
OL,8,Fearnings for the first six weeks, then
OL,9,F#187.18 for 33 weeks.
OL,11,FScott says the current system is just
OL,12,Fnot good enough
OL,14,FHe says "We just wanted to be a normal
OL,15,Ffamily at home and instead we were
OL,16,Fstuck in the neonatal unit not knowing
OL,17,Fwhat was going to happen. Tyler was
OL,18,Freally really poorly - he was having
OL,19,Fdifferent x-rays and scans - so it was
OL,20,Ftraumatic and difficult to comprehend"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
