OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,F"We live in a very progressive society
OL,7,F- but we have the worst paterntiy
OL,8,Fleave in Europe - its absoutely
OL,9,Fscandelous to think of really, and
OL,10,Fpeople don't see the impact it can
OL,11,Fhave on dads.
OL,13,F"The financial strain of having a baby
OL,14,Fis hard enough - then to feel the
OL,15,Fpressure of getting back to work
OL,16,Fbecause you're not on full
OL,17,Fwages...there's only so many plates
OL,18,Fyou can spin at the same time without
OL,19,Fone dropping, and when one drops it's
OL,20,Flike a domino effect, everything seems
OL,21,Fto fall apart at the same time"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
