OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FLouise Ramage agrees that her family
OL,7,Fwould have benefitted from better
OL,8,Fpaternity options.
OL,10,F"I've never been so lonely, it really
OL,11,Fimpacted my postpartum journey, so I
OL,12,Fended up with PTSD, post partum
OL,13,Fanxiety and post parrtum depression. I
OL,14,Ffeel like having more time with my
OL,15,Fhusband and not having to be concerend
OL,16,Fabout money and time, I think that
OL,17,Fwould have greatly imrproved that"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
