OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,F"It felt like we had a countdown
OL,7,Fgoing, because we knew we only had a
OL,8,Fshort window of time before Scott was
OL,9,Fgoing back to work. I remember being
OL,10,Fconcerned about how I would pick him
OL,11,Fup on my own, how I'd be able to
OL,12,Fchange him, if i was even able to walk
OL,13,Fdown the stairs, because I was really
OL,14,Freally unwell."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
