OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FThe Dad Shift is a campaign calling
OL,7,Ffor better paternity leave. They've
OL,8,Frecently organised the first national
OL,9,FDad's Strike and are pushing the
OL,10,FGovernment to improve the current
OL,11,Foffering, which they say is the worst
OL,12,Fin Europe.
OL,14,FGeorge Gabriel, Co-Founder of The Dad
OL,15,FShift says: "The system hasn't really
OL,16,Fchanged for about 20 years. It's far
OL,17,Fpast the point at which it was
OL,18,Fdefensible. We are bottom of the
OL,19,Fleague.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/14
