OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,F"But everyone could benefit from
OL,7,Ffixing this - not just mums, dads and
OL,8,Fbabies. Independent research suggests
OL,9,Fthat by improving the UK's paternity
OL,10,Fleave system, you can drive #2.6
OL,11,Fbillion of growth in the wider UK
OL,12,Feconomy and at a time when the country
OL,13,Freally needs it. This is a way to
OL,14,Finvest in families, just as we have to
OL,15,Finvest in rail, roads and buildings"
OL,17,FWhat is the Government planning to do
OL,18,Fabout it?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
