OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,FThe Government says it wants to
OL,7,Fsupport working families and
OL,8,Fbuisnesses, and is looking to
OL,9,Fmodernise the system across paternity,
OL,10,Fmaternity and shared parental leave in
OL,11,FBritain
OL,13,FThe Government has launched a wide-
OL,14,Franging review to consider how the
OL,15,Fcurrent system could be improved to
OL,16,Fbetter support working families and
OL,17,Fmeet the needs of the modern economy.
OL,19,FThe call for evidence ends on the 25th
OL,20,Fof August - and they want to hear from
OL,21,Fanyone with experience of the system.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
