OL,3,CUK fathers call for action over 'worst
OL,4,Cpaternity leave policy in Europe'
OL,6,F"We're very open minded at this stage.
OL,7,FWe've had lots of representations from
OL,8,Fpeople on different aspects of it, and
OL,9,Fwe hear that what we've got at the
OL,10,Fmoment is something that is a bit
OL,11,Fhotchpotch. It's been developed over
OL,12,Fmany years and it is quite difficult
OL,13,Ffor people to navigate. We're
OL,14,Fconscious of the fact we don't want to
OL,15,Fput more costs on businesses. But
OL,16,Fwe're also aware that lots of
OL,17,Fbusinesses feel that having an
OL,18,Fimproved parental leave system is a
OL,19,Fgood thing for them in terms of staff
OL,20,Fretention in particular"
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/14
